  "solutionJava": "public static int indexOfMaxValue(List<Integer> numbers) {\n  int bestIndex = 0;\n  for (int i = 1; i < numbers.size(); i += 1) {\n    if (numbers.get(i) > numbers.get(bestIndex)) {\n      bestIndex = i;\n    }\n  }\n  return bestIndex;\n}",
